title: Washington Adventist University President Weymouth Spence Joins the Montgomery County Chamber of Commerce Board of ...
text: ( Source : Washington Adventist University ) Takoma Park, MD ( October 14 , 2015 ) Washington Adventist University President Weymouth Spence , Ed.D. , R.T. , has been named to the Montgomery County Chamber of Commerce 's 2015-2016 Board of Directors .
